  "prompt": "What are some good online interior design courses?",
  "response": "There are several reputable online platforms where you can find good interior design courses. Here are some notable ones:\n\n1. **Udemy**: Udemy offers a variety of interior design courses for different skill levels. Some popular picks include \"Interior Design Basics,\" \"How to Work with Interior Design Styles Like a Pro,\" and \"Interior Design for Beginners.\"\n\n2. **Coursera**: Coursera offers courses from top universities and institutions. The \"Making Architecture\" course by IE School of Architecture & Design and \"Space Planning\" by the National Taiwan University are highly recommended.\n\n3. **Skillshare**: Skillshare has a range of interior design classes, focusing on specific aspects like color theory, space planning, and more. Courses like \"Interior Design Basics: Simple Steps to Perfect Your Space\" and \"Interior Design: Interior Decorate like a Boss!\" are popular.\n\n4. **MasterClass**: MasterClass offers in-depth courses taught by experts. Kelly Wearstler's \"Interior Design\" course is a standout, providing insights from a renowned designer.\n\n5. **NYIAD (New York Institute of Art and Design)**: NYIAD offers comprehensive accredited courses such as the \"Complete Course in Interior Design\" and specialized courses like \"Feng Shui Interior Design.\"\n\n6. **The Interior Design Institute**: This institute provides an online diploma course in Interior Design, which is comprehensive and suitable for aspiring professionals.\n\n7. **Domestika**: Domestika offers creative courses, including several on interior design. Courses like \"Interior Design: Create a Concept for Your Space\" and \"Interior Styling and Design\" are popular choices.\n\n8. **LinkedIn Learning**: LinkedIn Learning offers various interior design courses led by professionals. Courses like \"Designing a House to be a Home\" and \"Learning Interior Design\" are well-reviewed.\n\nWhen selecting a course, consider what specific skills or knowledge you're aiming to acquire and check reviews and ratings to ensure the course aligns with your objectives.",
